    <title>用 Hexo 搭建个人博客</title>
    <url>/posts/7780/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>做个人主页其实不是件困难的事，毕竟只要把很多东西当成黑箱来用即可。所以本文分为两大部分，第一大部分 <code>太长不看速通版</code> 是给性急的朋友，只要按步骤操作，不求甚解的话应该不到十五分钟就可以打好基本的框架，也就是够到能用的标准，后续只需写 <code>.md</code> 文件即可。</p>
<p>但就像大多数人使用 <code>LaTeX</code> 一样，大多数人确实不需要知道原理，能用即可；但少部分所谓『强迫症患者』或者有兴趣的人，也确实希望知其然的同时也知其所以然，后半部分即是为了满足这部分需求。</p>
<p>本文用 Hexo 搭建个人博客的逻辑主要如下：</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<ul>
<li>利用 GitHub 创建一个免费的站点 <code>usrname.github.io</code></li>
<li>利用 Hexo 在本地初始化，完成本地部署</li>
<li>利用 Hexo 的 deploy 插件，把本地文件部署到 GitHub 上，建立本地文件和站点的联系</li>
<li>后续只需用 hexo 创建 md 文件，并用任意编辑器写作，然后用 hexo『编译』，最后部署</li>
</ul>
<h1 id="tai-chang-bu-kan-su-tong-ban">太长不看速通版<a href="#tai-chang-bu-kan-su-tong-ban" class="header-anchor">#</a></h1>
<h2 id="guan-yu-chuang-jian-zhan-dian">关于创建站点<a href="#guan-yu-chuang-jian-zhan-dian" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<ol type="1">
<li><p>创建一个仓库（repository，简写为 repo），选为公开（public），名字格式为 <code>xxx.github.io</code>，其中 <code>xxx</code> 就是 GitHub 账户的用户名，例如本站就是 <code>mathirst.github.io</code></p></li>
<li><p>点击左侧导航栏里的 Pages，回头把 <code>branch</code> 设为 <code>gh-pages</code> （现在还没创建，所以还没得选）</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="dai-ma-he-ji">代码合集<a href="#dai-ma-he-ji" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 打开终端，如果没有特别设置，默认都在根目录</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装 homebrew （已有的话可以跳过）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># https://docs.brew.sh/Installation</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># macOS Requirements</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">##  A 64-bit Intel CPU or Apple Silicon CPU</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">##  macOS Big Sur (11) (or higher) </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">##  Command Line Tools (CLT) for Xcode (from xcode-select --install or https://developer.apple.com/download/all/) or Xcode </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">##  The Bourne-again shell for installation (i.e. bash) </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> HOMEBREW_BREW_GIT_REMOTE=<span class="string">"..."</span>  <span class="comment"># put your Git mirror of Homebrew/brew here</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> HOMEBREW_CORE_GIT_REMOTE=<span class="string">"..."</span>  <span class="comment"># put your Git mirror of Homebrew/homebrew-core here</span></span><br><span class="line">/bin/bash -c <span class="string">"<span class="subst">$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install.sh)</span>"</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 正文开始</span></span><br><span class="line">brew install node <span class="comment"># 用 brew 安装 npm</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo npm install -g hexo-cli <span class="comment"># 用 npm 安装 hexo</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo -v <span class="comment"># 查看 hexo 版本信息，其实就是确认一下安装有没有出错，可以直接跳过</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo init mathirst.github.io <span class="comment"># 在根目录下创建名为 github 主页链接的文件夹，并初始化</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> mathirst.github.io <span class="comment"># 用 cd（即change directory） 切换工作目录到刚刚创建的文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">npm install <span class="comment"># 激活 hexo 的一些设置</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save <span class="comment"># 安装部署到 GitHub 的插件，以支持 deploy 命令</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">open . <span class="comment"># 在 Finder 中打开这一文件夹，注意不要漏掉点号；然后编辑 _configure.yml 如下</span></span><br><span class="line">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ _config.yml ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Site</span></span><br><span class="line">title: 稻年</span><br><span class="line">subtitle:</span><br><span class="line">description: 不息，不止</span><br><span class="line">author: 稻年</span><br><span class="line">language: zh-CN <span class="comment"># 设置为中文后，诸如 tags, categories 都会被汉化</span></span><br><span class="line">timezone: </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># URL</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as 'http://yoursite.com/child' and root as '/child/'</span></span><br><span class="line">url: http://mathirst.github.io/</span><br><span class="line">root: /</span><br><span class="line">permalink: :year/:month/:day/:title/</span><br><span class="line">permalink_defaults:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Docs: &lt;http://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: &lt;https://github.com/mathirst/mathirst.github.io.git&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  branch: gh-pages </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 注意，我这里改成了 gh-pages 分支（branch），如果没有最后会自动创建</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 所以在 GitHub 中的设置里也要把 GitHub Pages 的默认分支改成 gh-pages</span></span><br><span class="line">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ _config.yml end ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 没写的都先不管，注意编辑时要去掉默认带的一些单引号 </span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">brew install gh <span class="comment"># 安装 gh 命令，因为登录会用到 gh</span></span><br><span class="line">gh auth login <span class="comment"># 登录到 GitHub，会输出一系列交互式的结果</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo generate &amp;&amp; hexo deploy <span class="comment"># 输出 html 等文件并部署（deploy）到 GitHub</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 或者</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy <span class="comment"># 区别是 clean = genearate + 清理缓存文件 db.json</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 或者</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy &amp;&amp; hexo server <span class="comment"># 多加一个 hexo server, 可以查看本地效果，按住 command+输出的链接，会自动打开本地网页</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在站点目录下，文件夹 source/_posts 下会有个默认生成的 hello-world.md，编辑该 md 并保存后，本地网页会实时更新，但若要在 GitHub 的站点里也显示，你必须重新部署到 GitHub。如果你使用了 hexo server，则需要按住 ctrl+C 来退出本地服务器，然后重新执行上述部署命令之一；不过也可以另外打开一个终端窗口（按住 cmd+T），然后 cd mathirst.github.io 切换到站点目录，执行 </span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 这样就可以保持本地服务器一直维持</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 下面则是进一步配置模板主题，我选的是 NexT</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span>  mathirst.github.io <span class="comment"># 确保工作路径没问题 </span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> &lt;https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-theme-next.git&gt; themes/NexT <span class="comment"># 下载主题文件到站点目录下的 themes/NexT （会自动创建这些文件夹）</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 再次打开站点目录 mathirst.github.io 下的站点配置文件 _config.yml，编辑如下</span></span><br><span class="line">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ _config.yml ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Extensions</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Plugins: &lt;http://hexo.io/plugins/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Themes: &lt;http://hexo.io/themes/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">theme: NexT</span><br><span class="line">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ _config.yml ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 之后打开刚刚下载的主题文件夹 mathirst.github.io/themes/NexT，里面也有个配置文件 _config.yml，为作区别，我们叫做 主题配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ _config.yml end ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Schemes</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Muse</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Mist</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#scheme: Pisces</span></span><br><span class="line">scheme: Gemini <span class="comment"># 设置主题的 scheme 为 Gemini</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">menu: <span class="comment"># 我选择显示了下述项目，首页</span></span><br><span class="line">  home: / || fa fa-home <span class="comment"># 首页</span></span><br><span class="line">  tags: /tags/ || fa fa-tags <span class="comment"># 标签</span></span><br><span class="line">  categories: /categories/ || fa fa-th <span class="comment"># 分类</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#archives: /archives/ || fa fa-archive</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#schedule: /schedule/ || fa fa-calendar</span></span><br><span class="line">  sitemap: /sitemap.xml || fa fa-sitemap <span class="comment"># 站点地图</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#commonweal: /404/ || fa fa-heartbeat</span></span><br><span class="line">  about: /about/ || fa fa-user <span class="comment"># 关于</span></span><br><span class="line">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ _config.yml end ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 到此就完成最简单的配置了！最后别忘了部署</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="xi-fen-jie-shao">细分介绍<a href="#xi-fen-jie-shao" class="header-anchor">#</a></h1>
<h2 id="chuang-jian-github-pages-zhan-dian">创建 GitHub Pages 站点<a href="#chuang-jian-github-pages-zhan-dian" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<p>首先在 GitHub 下要创建一个站点（website），后面命令行做的事不过是调用别人写好的模板（hexo）来配置我们的站点显示样式。这和 LaTeX 的内容与样式相分离的思想是一模一样的。</p>
<ol type="1">
<li>创建一个仓库（repository，简写为 repo），名字格式为 <code>xxx.github.io</code>，xxx 就是你想要的站点名字，比如我这里选的是 mathirst，而且如下图所示，GitHub 会自动检测是否重名（我这里是为了示范又重新打开了新建仓库的界面，由于我的站点已经存在，所以显示重名）。xxx 直接填你的 GitHub usrname。</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="/posts/7780/create-repo-name.png"></p>
<ol start="2" type="1">
<li>点击左侧导航栏里的 Pages，也就是对应了 <code>github.io</code> 的域名，使用这个叫做 GitHub Pages 的域名不需要支付任何费用，唯二的缺点是站点的名字必须和用户名一致，而且仓库必须公开，所以要免费改站点名字就必须改用户名，不然会看到下述界面，点击 Upgrade 就会弹出付费界面，年费48刀。</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="/posts/7780/create-repo-pages.png"> ## 安装 Hexo</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装 hexo</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo npm install -g hexo-cli </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看 hexo 版本信息</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="chuang-jian-ben-di-wen-jian-jia">创建本地文件夹<a href="#chuang-jian-ben-di-wen-jian-jia" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 用 hexo init 命令创建一个文件夹，名为 mathirst.github.io，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 同时在 GitHub 创建一个同名的 project，其中 mathirst 是我的 github 用户名，</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 这样可以方便记忆（完全是从命名角度来说取同一个名字）</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo init mathirst.github.io</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 终端下切换到刚创建的文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> yt8yt.github.io</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 激活 hexo 相关的一些设置</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="yun-xing-ce-shi-fu-wu-qi">运行测试服务器<a href="#yun-xing-ce-shi-fu-wu-qi" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 生成一个临时服务器，方便本地查看输出效果。输出为</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># INFO  Hexo is running at &lt;http://0.0.0.0:4000/&gt;. Press Ctrl+C to stop. </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 按住 cmd 点击上述链接，便会自动调用默认浏览器打开这一网页；</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 按住 ctrl+C 便可关闭这一临时服务器</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="she-zhi-zhan-dian-de-yi-xie-xin-xi">设置站点的一些信息<a href="#she-zhi-zhan-dian-de-yi-xie-xin-xi" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># vi 是调用 vim 来打开文件，然后可以用 vim 的方式来编辑该文件；</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 也可以直接双击该文件来用编辑器修改，例如默认的是XCode</span></span><br><span class="line">vi _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>注意：写 yml 文件时，注意去掉单引号，例如</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">description: xxx's personal blog </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#不能是</span><br><span class="line">description: ‘xxx's personal blog’</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>示例（没写出来的都可以不用改，取决于个人需求）</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span> <span class="string">_config.yml</span> <span class="string">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Site</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">Minhua</span> <span class="string">Cheng's</span> <span class="string">note</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">Minhua</span> <span class="string">Cheng's</span> <span class="string">personal</span> <span class="string">blog</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">Minhua</span> <span class="string">Cheng</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">MST</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># URL</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as '&lt;http://yoursite.com/child&gt;' and root as '/child/'</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">&lt;http://mathirst.github.io/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">root:</span> <span class="string">/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink:</span> <span class="string">:year/:month/:day/:title/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink_defaults:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="pei-zhi-shi-yong-git-de-xin-xi">配置使用 Git 的信息<a href="#pei-zhi-shi-yong-git-de-xin-xi" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装插件使得 hexo 可以部署到 git，执行一次即可</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 再次编辑 yml 配置文件，此时出现 Deployment 的配置</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>下面是示例</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span> <span class="string">_config.yml</span> <span class="string">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Docs: &lt;http://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">&lt;https://github.com/mathirst/mathirst.github.io.git&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">gh-pages</span> <span class="comment"># 注意，我这里改成了 gh-pages 分支（branch），如果没有最后会自动创建</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>所以在 GitHub 中的设置里也要把 GitHub Pages 的默认分支改成 gh-pages</p>
<h2 id="sheng-cheng-zhan-dian-qian-xian-watch">生成站点前先“watch”<a href="#sheng-cheng-zhan-dian-qian-xian-watch" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate --watch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="chuang-jian-xin-wang-ye-bing-bian-ji">创建新网页并编辑<a href="#chuang-jian-xin-wang-ye-bing-bian-ji" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建新网页，名为 first-post</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new first-post</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 或者</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new page </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 输出为</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># INFO  Created: ~/***/yt8yt.github.io/source/_posts/first-post.md</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 可以看到实际上是本地生成了一个 markdown 文件，所以可以直接编辑 markdown 来更改最终的输出内容</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="shan-chu-mo-ren-de-hello-world">删除默认的 hello world<a href="#shan-chu-mo-ren-de-hello-world" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<p>即删掉 <code>source/_posts/hello-world.md</code></p>
<h2 id="bu-shu-dao-github">部署到 GitHub<a href="#bu-shu-dao-github" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 首先登录 GitHub</span></span><br><span class="line">brew install gh <span class="comment"># 安装 gh 命令，因为登录会用到 gh</span></span><br><span class="line">gh auth login <span class="comment"># 登录到 GitHub，会输出一系列交互式的结果</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># What account do you want to log into? 选第一个 GitHub.com</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># What is your preferred protocol for Git operations? 我选的是 HTTPS</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Authenticate Git with your GitHub credentials? Yes</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># How would you like to authenticate GitHub CLI? 选 Login with a web browser</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 同时注意（终端里）后面就会给出验证码 First copy your one-time code: xxx</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Press Enter to open github.com in your browser... 回车在弹窗里输入这串验证码即可</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 完成登录</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 部署（deploy）到 GitHub</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo generate &amp;&amp; hexo deploy </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#或者</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy <span class="comment"># 区别是 clean = genearate + 清理缓存文件 db.json</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>注意：部署完刷新页面并不会立即有反应，需要等1-2分钟</p>
<h2 id="huan-zhu-ti">换主题<a href="#huan-zhu-ti" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<p>可用的主题列表见链接</p>
<p>https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/wiki/Themes</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 先下载主题，其中 </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># &lt;repository&gt; 就是 GitHub 页面里的连接</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># themes/&lt;theme-name&gt; 就是把主题下载到当前目录下的新文件夹 themes 里，并重命名为 theme-name</span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> &lt;repository&gt; themes/&lt;theme-name&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 具体来说，我用的是 NexT 主题，示例如下</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span>  mathirst.github.io <span class="comment"># 确保工作路径没问题 </span></span><br><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> &lt;https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-theme-next.git&gt; themes/NexT</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 再改 yml 配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">vi _config.yml</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ _config.yml ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Extensions</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Plugins: &lt;http://hexo.io/plugins/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Themes: &lt;http://hexo.io/themes/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">theme: NexT</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="ce-shi-chang-yong-ming-ling">测试常用命令<a href="#ce-shi-chang-yong-ming-ling" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 仅本地测试</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo server</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 同步到主页</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy &amp;&amp; hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="bao-cuo">报错<a href="#bao-cuo" class="header-anchor">#</a></h2>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Error: ENOTEMPTY: directory not empty, <span class="built_in">rmdir</span> <span class="string">'/Users/chengminhua/mathirst.github.io/.deploy_git/archives'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>直接到 deploy_git 文件夹下把文件都删干净，再重新执行 <code>hexo deploy</code> 即可</p>
